          	            	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-13080.htm">高中通訊  VIII.故王江長老小傳 [ Ko Tiong Thong-sìn VIII. Kò͘ Ông Kang Tiúⁿ-ló Sió-toān ]</a></span>
